sequenceDiagram
actor Client
participant API as PlaceAPI (Presentation)
participant Facade as HBnBFacade (Business)
participant PRepo as PlaceRepository (Persistence)
participant DB as Database

Client->>API: GET /places
API->>Facade: list_places()
Facade->>PRepo: list_all()
PRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM places
DB-->>PRepo: rows or error

alt db error
  PRepo-->>Facade: error
  Facade-->>API: 500 Server Error
  API-->>Client: 500 Server Error
else ok
  PRepo-->>Facade: places[]
  Facade-->>API: 200 OK (places[])
  API-->>Client: 200 OK (places[])
end
